{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Decimate Drive features frantic chases which are as fun as they are fatal. Run for your life as every car in the city hunts you down.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Run from cover to cover. Constantly use your environment to your advantage as you go from wide-open parking lots to claustrophobic alleys.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2427950/extras/DecimateDrive-SnowPlow.png?t=1728665150\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each enemy is deadly in its own way. Unwieldy trucks charge straight for you while unassuming sedans quietly sneak up on you. Survive long enough to find out how you ended up in a killer car infested city. Decimate Drive, set in a desolate city in the cold north of the United States, features a dark surreal story-line.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2427950/extras/DecimateDrive-Phone.png?t=1728665150\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Story mode featuring a dark surreal story line</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Additional Backroads story mode featuring a new setting and new killer cars</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Additional Hit &amp; Run arcade mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fast-paced frantic gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">New game plus, collectibles and killer car gallery</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">15+ killer cars and 25+ desolate locations</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2427950/extras/DecimateDrive-Hotel.png?t=1728665150\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Backroads story mode</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The additional (short) story mode Backroads is set in a remote backcountry where killer cars rely on heavy for to remain unseen. It features six new locations and six new killer cars.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Hit &amp; Run arcade mode</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Go for a new high score while being chased by killer cars. All the while you have to stop the timer from running out. And deal with random buffs and debuffs. It's fast paced, unpredictable and chaotic. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">What's next?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">For now there are no new content updates planned for Decimate Drive.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2427950/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1728665150","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2427950/page.bg.jpg?t=1728665150","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2427950/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1728665150","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2427950/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1728665150","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[2,5],"notes":"This game features mature content not appropriate for all ages, or may not be appropriate for viewing at work. Frequent Violence or Blood, General Mature Content."},"demos":[{"appid":2654100,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Decimate Drive features frantic chases which are as fun as they are fatal. Run for your life as every car in the city hunts you down.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Run from cover to cover. Constantly use your environment to your advantage as you go from wide-open parking lots to claustrophobic alleys.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store